scene.message:
Mark: Wh-what is that...{nl}
No way... that's{nl}
our city...!{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: Yes, your city.{nl}
It is my new{nl}
residence now...{waitkey}{clearbox}I think I'll call it{nl}
'Deva Yuga.'{waitkey}{nl}
A name fit to herald{nl}
a shining new age...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: G-gulp...{nl}
The city just{nl}
vanished...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: No way...{nl}
Everyone who was there...{nl}
they all just died?{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: Hmhm...{wait_fr:79}Ha-hahha!{nl}
This 'Mirror of Chaos' is{nl}
exactly what I sought!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Magnificent...{nl}
Unlike that puny compact,{nl}
its power is plain to see!{waitkey}{clearbox}Without the Deva System,{nl}
I now hold the power to{nl}
cross worlds and grant wishes!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: I see... It's{nl}
coming together now.{nl}
The compact, the Deva System{nl}
were all just stepping stones.{waitkey}And so...{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: I shall become the{nl}
god of this world.{nl}
A god has but one task...{waitkey}To bring the rod of judgment{nl}
down upon foolish mankind!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: I see... so you...{wait_fr:79}{nl}
you mean to slaughter{nl}
all of humanity...{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: Now I return to{nl}
the real world.{nl}
Do you hate me?{nl}
If so, then come after me...{waitkey}Once you've beaten this one!{waitkey}{ret}

Kandori: What one desires{nl}
is never easily won.{nl}
And yet...{waitkey}{clearbox}The joy of grasping it{nl}
after every obstacle{nl}
is supreme...{nl}
Take it as divine revelation!{waitkey}{ret}

Demon: Now then, showtime.{nl}
I'll make you dance...{nl}
the dance of death!!{waitkey}{ret}
